    <h5 class="phase-title show-for-small">Phase I - Research and Feasibility Report</h5>
    <p>We meet with you to review your ideas and goals for your small home and draft a site plan and budget. We research zoning and permitting requirements and give you a summary of city fees and project constraints. You will meet with one of our architects to start the design process.</p>
